INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('67e7b228-5892-4f26-87fd-b9c7ffd406d2', '《水浒传》[卷74]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:08:38', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '74', '\r\n    叭叫庄客：“不要开门！”\r\n\r\n    掇条梯子上墙打一看时，只见是华阴县尉在马上，引着两个都头，带着三四百士兵，围住庄院。\r\n\r\n    史进及三个头领只管叫苦。\r\n\r\n    外面火光中照见钢叉，朴刀，五股寸，留客住，摆得似麻林一般。\r\n\r\n    两个都头口里叫道：“不要走了强贼！”\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'Zhan called Zhuangke: &quot;Do not open the door!&quot; When the curtain ladder took a look at the wall, I saw that Huayin County was lying on the horse, leading the two capitals, with three or four hundred soldiers, surrounding the Zhuang Yuan. Shi Jin and the three chiefs only complained. Outside the fire in the steel fork, Park knife, five-inch inch, stay guest to live, placed like an ordinary forest. Both of them cried, &quot;Don&#39;t go strong thief!&quot;', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('688850ce-9385-4001-814b-99784eef6618', '新媒介技术挑战下当代文化自信的可能', '人文', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-05-09 12:59:04', '2018-05-20', '1', '50', '1', '0', '1', '0', '文化自信”问题包含理论和实践两个方面的研究路径。后者充分注意到了“文化自信”所具有的当代性和实践性。新媒介技术正在对文化意义上的当代性和实践性提出挑战：它引发了自然观、社会观和艺术观的巨大改变。面对这一挑战，新文化可以从自然整体观、社会包容观、艺术生成观三个方面来获得自信的可能', null, 'The problem of &quot;cultural self-confidence&quot; contains both theoretical and practical research paths. The latter fully takes note of the contemporary and practical nature of &quot;cultural self-confidence.&quot; New media technologies are challenging contemporary and practical aspects of cultural significance: It has triggered a tremendous change in the outlook on nature, society, and arts. Faced with this challenge, the new culture can gain confidence from three aspects: the overall view of nature, the concept of social inclusion, and the concept of artistic generation.', '0');
