INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('8ff57c2e-ae40-4993-8c41-4e53590a8876', '《水浒传》[卷14]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:05:23', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '14', '\r\n    王都尉出来见了干人，看了令旨，随即上马，来到九大王府前，下了马，入宫来见了端王。\r\n\r\n    端王大喜，称谢两般玉玩器，入席，饮宴间，端王说道：“这高俅踢得两脚好气球，孤欲索此人做亲随，如何？”\r\n\r\n    王都尉答道：“既殿下欲用此人，就留在宫中伏侍殿下。”\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'When Wang Tufan came out to meet the cadres, he read the order and immediately launched it. He came to the front of the nine great palaces and set a horse and entered the palace to meet the king. End of the day, Wang Xixi praised the two jade players. When they attended the banquet, the king said: “This Gaochun played a good two-legged balloon and asked for this person to do so.” Wang Duxi replied: His Royal Highness wants to use this person and stays in his palace to stay with him.&quot;', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('9227fbf2-b1ce-4b3c-9a83-33302e04da99', '《水浒传》[卷57]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:07:40', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '57', '\r\n    史进回到庄上，把陈达绑在庭心内柱上，等待一发拿了那贼首，一并解官请赏；且把酒来赏了众人，教且权散。\r\n\r\n    众人喝采：“不枉了史大郎如此豪杰！”\r\n\r\n    休说众人欢喜饮酒。\r\n\r\n    却说朱武、杨春，两个正在寨里猜疑，捉摸不定，且教小喽罗再去探听消息。只见回去的人牵着空马，奔到山前，只叫道：“苦也！陈家哥哥不听二位哥哥所说，送了性命！”\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'Shi Jin returned to Zhuangshang and tied Chen Da to the inner pillar of the court. He waited for the head of the thief and took the reward with him. He also offered wine to the people, taught and dispersed. The crowd applauded: &quot;If you don&#39;t know how great Shi Dalang is!&quot; Hugh said that everyone was happy about drinking. It was said that Zhu Wu and Yang Chun were both skeptical and unpredictable in Zhaili, and Xiao Xiaolu was asked to listen to the news again. The man who only went back took the empty horse and ran to the front of the mountain. He only called out: &quot;Bitter! Chen brother did not listen to what his two brothers said and sent his life!&quot;', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('92824513-d86c-4ca8-b13c-676a3a6367d9', '《水浒传》[卷70]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:08:25', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '70', '\r\n    却说庄客王四一觉直睡到二更方醒，觉得看见月光微微照在身上，吃了一惊，跳将起来，却见四边都是松树；便去腰里摸时，搭和书都不见了；四下里寻时，只见空搭在莎草上。\r\n\r\n    王四只管叫苦，寻思道：“银子不打紧，这封回书却怎生得好？．．．正不知被甚人拿去了？．．．”眉头一纵，计上心来，自道：“若回去庄上说脱了回书，大郎必然焦躁，定是赶我出来；不如只说不曾有回书，那里查照？”\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'It is said that Zhuang Kewang&#39;s four-year-old sleeps until he wakes up until he wakes up and feels that he saw the moonlight shining slightly on his body. He was taken aback and jumped up, but he saw pine trees on all sides; when he went to touch his waist, he took both books and books. It was gone; when he looked around, he saw the air ride over the sedge. The king of four just ranted and wondered: &quot;The silver does not matter, but how can this book be born well?... I do not know if I was taken away?...&quot; The brow was a vertical one. &quot;If you go back to Zhuangshang and say that you have come back to the book, Dalang must be embarrassed and you must drive me out. It&#39;s better to just say that there was no reply.', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('92941ee9-8a6b-45e0-81d0-b22eb899ca66', '《斗罗大陆序章》[卷2]', '小说', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 16:39:24', '2018-05-26', '0', '400', '0', '0', '1', '2', '\r\n    他今年二十九岁，因出生不久就进入唐门，在外门弟子的辈分中排名第三，因此外门弟子称他一声三少。当然，到了内门弟子口中，就变成了唐三。\r\n\r\n    唐门从建立时开始就分为内外两门，外门都是外姓或被授予唐姓的弟子，而内门，则是唐门直系所属，家族传承。\r\n\r\n    此时，唐三脸上的表情很丰富，时而笑，时而哭，但无论如何，都无法掩盖他的那发自内心的兴奋。\r\n', 'def3130a-a4ae-4589-8f8e-e19cb9c60f29', 'He was 29 years old this year. He entered Tangmen soon after his birth. He ranked third in the generation of his disciples, so his disciples called him three. Of course, when he reached the inner door, he became Tang. From the time of its establishment, Tangmen was divided into two internal and external doors. The external doors were all surnames or disciples who were given Tang&#39;s surname. The internal gates were directly subordinate to Tangmen and the family inherited. At this time, Tang&#39;s face was full of expressions, laughing and crying sometimes, but in any case, can not cover his excitement from the heart.', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('9506d4eb-62c8-40cb-84af-277571d41a57', '《水浒传》[卷23]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:05:51', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '23', '    挑了担儿，跟在马后，趁五更天色未明，乘势出了西华门，取路望延安府来。且说z茧p军买了福物煮熟，在庙等到已牌，也不见来。\r\n\r\n    李牌心焦，走回到家中寻时，只见锁了门，两头无路，寻了半日并无有人。\r\n\r\n    看看待晚，岳庙里张牌疑忌，一直奔回家来，又和李牌寻了一黄昏。\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'After picking up the children and following the horses, it was not clear whether the sky was brighter or brighter. He took the Xihua Gate and took the road to look for Yanan. And said that the z茧p army had bought good things and cooked them, and waited until the cards had been sold at the temple. When Li returned to his home and found it, he saw that he had locked the door and he had no way to go. There was no person searching for half a day. Look to stay late, in the Yuemusi, there was a sign of misgivings. He ran all the way home and found a night with Li.', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('95f64675-a3c4-4001-847c-c8a0efb5a54d', '《红楼梦》[卷6]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-18 09:38:49', '2018-05-27', '0', '455', '0', '0', '1', '6', '样女子，或情或痴，或小才微善。我纵然抄去，也算不得一种奇书。”石头果然答\r\n道：“我师何必太痴!我想历来野史的朝代，无非假借汉、唐的名色；莫如我这石头\r\n所记不借此套，只按自己的事体情理，反倒新鲜别致。况且那野史中，或讪谤君相，\r\n或贬人妻女，奸淫凶恶，不可胜数；更有一种风月笔墨，其淫秽污臭最易坏人子弟。\r\n', 'a26059ca-ddc9-4f05-a733-d1421bc7f438', 'Like a woman, or love or delusion, or a little talented. Even if I copy it, it would not be a strange book. The stone replied: &quot;My teacher must be too crazy! I think the history of the dynasty has nothing to do, but under the guise of the Han and Tang&#39;s name; as the stone I do not remember this set, just according to their own circumstances, but fresh Chic. Moreover, in the history of the wilderness, either the gentleman or the degrading wife and daughter, the adulterous and vicious woman is invincible. There is also a kind of lunatic brushstroke and ink, and its obscene and foul stench is the most vulnerable to the children of the bad.', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('97dfbee9-8850-46f5-b21b-3a16ecf3054f', '《水浒传》[卷21]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:05:48', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '21', '\r\n    王进道：“不妨。母亲放心，儿子自有道理措置他。”\r\n\r\n    当下日晚未昏。\r\n\r\n    王进先叫张牌入来，分付道：“你先吃了些晚饭，我使你一处去干事。”\r\n\r\n    张牌道：“教头使小人那里去？”\r\n\r\n    王进道：“我因前日患病许下酸枣门外岳庙里香愿，明日早要去烧炷头香。你可今晚先去分付庙祝，教他来日早些开庙门，等我来烧炷头香，就要三牲献刘李王。你就庙里歇了等我。”\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'Wang Jin said: &quot;Maybe. My mother is relieved. My son treated him with reason.&quot; Wang Jin first called the card and paid for it: &quot;You have some supper, I will make you go to the office.&quot; Zhang card said: &quot;Teacher head to the villain to go?&quot; Wang Jin said: &quot;I suffer from illness the day before Under the wild jujube at the door outside the Yuemiao Temple, I would like to burn the taro-flavored incense tomorrow morning.You may go to pay the temple wish tonight and teach him to open the temple earlier in the day. King Li, you stopped waiting for me in the temple.”', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('97ffa77b-473e-401f-8635-2b1657bf78cc', '商业计划书翻译[卷1]', '商业', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-05-09 12:29:22', '2018-08-10', '1', '50', '1', '0', '1', '1', '项目地域：北京\r\n\r\n报告用途：立项、融资\r\n\r\n项目简介：\r\n\r\n“互联网+食品安全”平台以《食品安全法》为依据，积极顺应互联网时代新变化，探索“互联网+食品安全”监管新思路，以大数据、信息化为支撑，创建具有社会共治特征，全流程可透明、全业态可覆盖、全链条可监督、全社会可参与、全方位可评价的体系，搭建起监管者、生产经营者、社会公众多方共治共赢平台，改善政府监管方式，创新食品安全风险治理机制，提升食品安全风险治理能力。\r\n', 'c690b2bb-73ba-43f5-aa30-ae5c578356b5', 'Project Area: Beijing Report Usage: Project, Financing Project Description: &quot;Internet + food safety&quot; platform based on the &quot;Food Safety Law&quot;, actively respond to the new changes in the Internet era, explore new ideas for &quot;Internet + food safety&quot; supervision, with big data , Informatization as a support, the establishment of a system with the characteristics of social co-governance, full flow can be transparent, the whole business can be covered, the whole chain can be supervised, the whole society can participate, all-round evaluative system, build up regulators, production operators, society The public has jointly managed a win-win platform, improved government supervision methods, innovated food safety risk management mechanisms, and improved food safety risk management capabilities.', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('9838d7af-5b9e-4df9-a80e-89c94d6a89f8', '《斗罗大陆序章》[卷4]', '小说', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 16:39:30', '2018-05-26', '0', '400', '0', '0', '1', '4', '\r\n    这些唐门长老的修为，无一不是已臻化境，只是转眼的工夫，他们就已经来到了山顶。\r\n\r\n    外门弟子见到内门长老，只有跪倒迎接的份，但此时，唐三却没有动，他只是静静的看着这些脸色凝重的长老来到自己面前，挡住了所有的去路，而在他背后，是鬼见愁。\r\n\r\n    放下三朵佛怒唐莲，唐三投下最后那恋恋不舍的一眼，嘴角处流露出一丝欣慰的微笑，他毕竟成功了，努力了二十年，他终于完成了这唐家外门暗器的巅峰之作，那种满足的成就，是无法用言语来形容的。\r\n', 'def3130a-a4ae-4589-8f8e-e19cb9c60f29', 'These elders of the Tangmen were all devastated, but they only came to an instant. They had already reached the top of the mountain. The outside door disciple saw the elders at the inner gate, but only took part in the meeting. But at this time, Tang San did not move. He just quietly watched these dignified elders come to him and blocked all the way. Behind him, is a ghost. Put down the three Buddha anger Tanglian, Tang San cast a last reluctant glance, mouth showing a smile of gratification, after all, he succeeded, and worked hard for 20 years, he finally completed the top of this Tang home screen hidden weapon As a result of that satisfaction, it is impossible to describe it in words.', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('9caa7ef2-6673-412e-8741-daf0f5fe3e1e', '《三国演义第一章》[卷7]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 16:57:43', '2018-05-12', '0', '500', '0', '0', '1', '7', '\r\n    时张角贼众十五万，植兵五万，相拒于广宗，未见胜负。植谓玄德曰：“我今围贼在此，贼弟张梁、张宝在颍川，与皇甫嵩、朱俊对垒。汝可引本部人马，我更助汝一千官军，前去颍川打探消息，约期剿捕。”玄德领命，引军星夜投颍川来。\r\n\r\n    时皇甫嵩、朱俊领军拒贼，贼战不利，退入长社，依草结营。嵩与俊计曰：“贼依草结营，当用火攻之。”遂令军士，每人束草一把，暗地埋伏。其夜大风忽起。二更以后，一齐纵火，嵩与俊各引兵攻击贼寨，火焰张天，贼众惊慌，马不及鞍，人不及甲，四散奔走。\r\n', '35893177-d499-4d71-9918-f1a9d79f3d7d', 'At the time, Zhang Chao’s thieves were 150,000, and he was planted with 50,000 soldiers. He was rejected by Guangzong and had no chance of winning. It is said that Xuande said: &quot;I am a thief here, and the thieves Zhang Liang and Zhang Bao are in the Chuanchuan River, and they are against Huangfu and Zhu Jun. You can quote the head of the troops and I even help a thousand troops to go and see you. Chuan inquire about the news, about the period of arrest.” Xuan De lead, cited military star night to come to Sichuan. When Huangfu and Zhu Jun led the army to reject the thief, the thief warfare was unfavorable. They retired to the Changsha Club and settled the camp. Yan and Jun Jiong said: &quot;The thief relies on grass camp, when it is attacked with fire.&quot; He ordered the sergeant to sow each one and secretly ambush them. It was suddenly blown up by the night. After the second and later, all arson was accompanied. Jun and Jun cited the soldiers and attacked the thieves. The flames were Zhang Tian, ​​the thieves were panic-stricken, the horses were not saddles, and people were less than one.', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('a01b1a07-d16b-4382-b8e5-d1b164d03eef', '《水浒传》[卷19]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:05:43', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '19', '\r\n    王进又告道：“太尉呼唤，不敢不来。”\r\n\r\n    高殿帅大怒∶喝令：“左右！拿下！加力与我打这厮！”\r\n\r\n    众多牙将都是和王进好的，只得与军正司同告道：“今日是太尉上任好日头，权免此人这一次。”\r\n\r\n    高太尉喝道：“你这贼配军！且看众将之面饶恕你今日！明日却和你理会！”王进谢罪罢，起来抬头看了，认得是高俅；出得衙门，叹口气道：“我的性命今番难保了！俺道是甚么高殿帅，却原来正是东京帮闲的圆社高二！比先时曾学使棒，被我父亲一棒打翻，三四个月将息不起。有此之仇，他今日发迹，得做殿帅府太尉，正待要报仇。我不想正属他管！自古道∶“不怕官，只怕管。”俺如何与他争得？怎生奈何是好？”回到家中，闷闷不已，对娘说知此事。\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'Wang Jin also said: &quot;Toooo call, dare not come.&quot; Gao Dianshuai furious: drink: &quot;Left and right! Take down! Afterburner and I fight this!&quot; Many teeth will be good and Wang Jin, Only with the military commander, he told the reporter: “Today is a good day to take advantage of this, and it is not necessary for this person to take this time.” Gao Taizhang shouted: “You are a thief with a military! The audience will forgive you today! Today will be tomorrow. And you care!” Wang Jin Xie sigh stopped, looked up and saw, knowing is high-pitched; out loud enough, sighed and said: “My life is hard to protect this time! What is the hallway Shuai handsome, but it was Tokyo is to help The circle club senior 2. I was overwhelmed by my father and was overwhelmed by my father&#39;s stick, and would not be able to pay for it for three or four months. With this revenge, he made a fortune today, and he has to be the commander-in-chief of the palace and is waiting to be done. Revenge.I don’t want to be his manager! Since ancient times: “I’m afraid of officials, but I’m afraid to control. &quot;How did you fight with him? How can you be good?&quot; When he got home, he was sullen and said to his mother.', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('a2fa0910-f296-41e0-8e1b-deb7eecc234b', '《水浒传》[卷3]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:04:54', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '3', '\r\n    绑来哲宗天子因拜南郊，感得风调雨顺，放宽恩，大赦天下，那高俅在临淮州因得了赦宥罪犯，思量要回东京。\r\n\r\n    这柳世权却和东京城里金梁桥下开生药铺的董将仕是亲戚，写了一封书札，收拾些人事盘缠，赍发高俅回东京投奔董将仕家过活。\r\n\r\n    当时高俅辞了柳大郎，背上包裹，离了临淮州，迤逦回到东京，迳来金梁桥下董生药家下了这一封书。\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'The tyrannical son of Zizezong was sent to the southern suburbs to feel good-weathered, to relax grace, and to conquer the world. The high-minded monk was found in Linhuai, and he thought that he would return to Tokyo. Liu Shiquan was a relative of Dong Genshi who opened a pharmacy under the Jinliang Bridge in Tokyo. He wrote a book, packed up some personnel, and sent Gao Yao to return to Tokyo and defected to his family. At the time, Gao Gao resigned from Liu Dalang, wrapped his back and left Lin Huaizhou. When he returned to Tokyo, he was given a book under Dong Liang Yao&#39;s family under Jinliang Bridge.', '0');
