INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('b6214ced-1e3f-4979-bb6e-296713b97132', '《三国演义第一章》[卷8]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-05-09 12:19:43', '2018-05-12', '1', '500', '1', '0', '1', '8', '\r\n    却说玄德引关、张来颍川，听得喊杀之声，又望见火光烛天，急引兵来时，贼已败散。玄德见皇甫嵩、朱俊，具道卢植之意。嵩曰：“张梁、张宝势穷力乏，必投广宗去依张角。玄德可即星夜往助。”玄德领命，遂引兵复回。得到半路，只见一簇军马，护送一辆槛车，车中之囚，乃卢植也。玄德大惊，滚鞍下马，问其缘故。植曰：“我围张角，将次可破；因角用妖术，未能即胜。朝廷差黄门左丰前来体探，问我索取贿赂。我答曰：‘军粮尚缺，安有余钱奉承天使？’左丰挟恨，回奏朝廷，说我高垒不战，惰慢军心；因此朝廷震怒，遣中郎将董卓来代将我兵，取我回京问罪。”张飞听罢，大怒，要斩护送军人，以救卢植。玄德急止之曰：“朝廷自有公论，汝岂可造次？”军士簇拥卢植去了。关公曰：“卢中郎已被逮，别人领兵，我等去无所依，不如且回涿郡。”玄德从其言，遂引军北行。行无二日，忽闻山后喊声大震。玄德引关、张纵马上高冈望之，见汉军大败，后面漫山塞野，黄巾盖地而来，旗上大书“天公将军”。玄德曰：“此张角也！可速战！”三人飞马引军而出。张角正杀败董卓，乘势赴来，忽遇三人冲杀，角军大乱，败走五十余里。\r\n', '35893177-d499-4d71-9918-f1a9d79f3d7d', 'It was said that Xuande leaded the offensive and Zhang Laishi Chuanchuan, heard the sound of cry, and saw the flames and candlelight. Xuande see Huangfu, Zhu Jun, with the meaning of Lu Zhi. He said: &quot;Zhang Liang and Zhang Baoxi are poor and lack power. They must cast Guangzong to go according to Zhang Jiao. Xuande will be able to help the starry night.&quot; After getting halfway, I saw a group of military horses and escorted a car. The prisoner in the car was Lu Zhiye. Xuande shocked and saddled the horse and asked why. Vegetable 曰 曰 “ “ “ 我 “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ “ 我 我 我 我 我 我 我 我There is money to flatter the angel? “Zuo Feng hated it and played it back at the court. He said that I was not at war and was inactive. Therefore, the court was furious, and demobilized Zhong Zhuo and Dong Zhuolai took me on behalf of the PLA. He took me back to Beijing and asked for guilt.” Fighting, anger, and escorting the soldiers to rescue Lu Zhi. Xuande rushed to stop: &quot;The court has its own public opinion, you can make times?&quot; Sergeants surrounded Lu Zhi went. Guan Gongyi: “Lu Zhonglang has been arrested. Others lead the troops. I waited for nowhere and was better than returning to the county.” Xuande said