INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('bca31de7-7dbd-48f5-b6d3-dcf12c14e3df', '《水浒传》[卷67]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:08:18', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '67', '\r\n    荏苒光阴，时遇八月中秋到来。\r\n\r\n    史进要和三人说话，约至十五夜来庄上赏月饮酒，先使庄客王四带一封请书直至少华山上请朱武，陈达，杨春，来庄上赴席。\r\n\r\n    王四驰书迳到山寨里，见了三位头领，下了来书。\r\n\r\n    朱武看了大喜。\r\n\r\n    三个应允，随即写封回书，赏了王四五两银子，吃了十来碗酒。\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'Slightly time, when the arrival of the Mid-Autumn Festival in August. Shi Jin will speak with the three people. He will visit the village on the 15th night and enjoy drinking on the moon. He will first bring Zhuang Kewang with one of his books and ask him at least to invite Zhu Wu, Chen Da, and Yang Chun to attend the banquet. When Wang Sichi went to the cottage in the book, he met three chiefs and wrote down. Zhu Wu looked overjoyed. Three promises were made and the book was written back, rewarding the king with four or five silver coins and eating ten bowls of wine.', '0');
