INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('ccf93b77-2fee-40eb-9b96-003b02efb3f3', '《水浒传》[卷25]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:05:57', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '25', '\r\n    在路一月有馀，忽一日，天色将晚，王进挑着担儿跟在娘的马后，口里与母亲说道：“天可怜见！惭愧了我母子两个脱了这天罗地网之厄！此去延安府不远了，高太尉便要差拿我也拿不着了！”\r\n\r\n    母子二人欢喜，在路上不觉错过了宿头，“走了这一晚，不遇着一处村坊，那里去投宿是好？．．．”正没理会处，只见远远地林子里闪出一道灯光来。\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'In the month of January, when the road is late, the sky will be late. Wang Jin will be carrying her mother and her mother&#39;s horse. He will say with his mother in the mouth: “Hey, see you! My mother and son have taken off from this day. This is not a long journey to Yan&#39;an. Gao Taiyi will have to take me away!” The mother and son rejoiced and missed the head on the road. “After this evening, I didn’t encounter a village house. Is it good to stay there?...” I just ignored and saw a light coming from far away in the woods.', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('cd7ab8d7-c5fe-49f4-b802-35cffb6661bb', '《水浒传》[卷68]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:08:21', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '68', '\r\n    王四相别了回庄，一面走着，被山风一吹，酒却涌上来，踉踉跄跄，一步一颠；走不得十里之路，见座林子，奔到里面，望着那绿茸茸莎草地上扑地倒了。\r\n\r\n    原来兔李吉正在那坡下张兔儿，认得是史家庄上王四，赶入林子里来扶他，那里扶得动，只见王四搭里出银子来。\r\n\r\n    李吉寻思道：“这厮醉了，．．．那里讨得许多？．．．何不拿他些？”\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'Wang Sixiang did not return to the village. As he walked and was blown by the mountain breeze, the wine rushed up and hesitated, step by step. He walked ten miles down the road and saw Linzi. He rushed to the inside and looked at the green. The grass fell on the ground. The original rabbit Li Ji was a rabbit under the slope. He recognized Shijiazhuang as a king and drove into the woods to help him. He could move there. Li Ji thought: &quot;This is drunk, ... is there a lot to ask? ... Why don&#39;t you take them?&quot;', '0');
