INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('e02a33c5-5292-497d-affe-015d2c309646', '《水浒传》[卷40]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:06:43', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '40', '\r\n    那后生又拜了王进。\r\n\r\n    太公道：“教头在上∶老汉祖居在这华阴县界，前面便是少华山。这村便唤做史家村，村中总有三四百家都姓史。老汉的儿子从小不务农业，只爱刺枪使棒；母亲说他不得，一气死了。老汉只得随他性子，不知使了多少钱财投师父教他；又请高手匠人与他剌了这身花绣，肩胸膛，总有九条龙。满县人口顺，都叫他做九纹龙史进。教头今日既到这里，一发成全了他亦好。老汉自当重重酬谢。”王进大喜道：“太公放心；既然如此说时，小人一发教了令郎方去。”\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'After that, they also worshipped Wang Jin. Taigong said: &quot;Teacher&#39;s head is on: The old man&#39;s ancestral home is in this Huayin County boundary, in front of which is Shaohua Mountain. This village will call Shijia Village. There are always three or four hundred family names in the village. The old man&#39;s son has never been a farmer since childhood. Only the love of stabbing the gun, the mother said he was not allowed to die, the old man had to follow his temper, I do not know how much money to vote for Master to teach him, and invited master craftsmen and he married this flower embroidered, shoulders chest, total There are nine dragons. The population of Manchu County is smooth, and they are all called him to be a nine-grain dragon. Jin Dao’s head is here today and his success is good. The old man has to reward him with gratitude.” Wang Jin rejoiced: “Taigong is assured; When we say this, the villain teaches the franchistory once.&quot;', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('e15cf55c-46ff-4c09-8851-050c3d135622', '《水浒传》[卷46]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:06:58', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '46', '\r\n    史进跳起身来，转过树背后，打一看时，认得是猎户兔李吉。\r\n\r\n    史进喝道：“李吉，张我庄内做甚么？莫不是来相脚头！”\r\n\r\n    李吉向前声诺道：“大郎，小人要寻庄上矮邱乙郎吃碗酒，因见大郎在此乘凉，不敢过来冲撞。”\r\n\r\n    史进道：“我且问你∶往常时你只是担些野味来我庄上卖，我又不曾亏了你，如何一向不将来卖与我？敢是欺负我没钱？”\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'Shi Jin jumped up and turned behind the tree. When he had a look at it, he recognized the Orion rabbit Li Ji. Shi Jin shouted: &quot;Li Ji, Zhang Zhuang inside to do? Is not come to the stage!&quot; Li Ji forward sound promise: &quot;Dalang, the villain to find Zhuang Shang Dzu Qiu Lang to eat a bowl of wine, because see Dalang In this cold weather, I dared not come in.&quot; Shi Jindao said: &quot;I ask you: When you&#39;re used to, you just have to take some game and sell it to me. I&#39;ve never lost you. How have you never sold me? Will you be bullied? No money?&quot;', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('e26330da-54af-4473-b038-0dfdc5651d95', '文化消费与美国小说的大众想象', '人文', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 16:23:25', '2018-05-25', '0', '100', '0', '0', '1', '0', '在大众文化背景下，美国小说的产生、传播和接受很大程度上受到文化消费市场和大众需求的影响，表现之一就是在大众文化发展较为完整、文化产业十分发达的美国，小说创作受到了市场导向以及接受主体文化消费习惯和心理的制约。同时，美国小说在表达大众想象上也保持了其主体性、自主性和人文精神的内涵', null, 'Under the background of popular culture, the production, dissemination and acceptance of American novels are largely influenced by the cultural consumer market and the needs of the general public. One of the manifestations is that in the United States where the development of popular culture is relatively complete and the cultural industry is very developed, the creation of novels is affected. Market orientation and acceptance of the subject&#39;s cultural consumption habits and psychological constraints. At the same time, the American novel also maintains the connotation of its subjectivity, autonomy and humanistic spirit in expressing the public imagination.', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('e64e10f7-30ec-4776-9751-25fd93cfffc6', '《水浒传》[卷66]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:08:14', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '66', '\r\n    小喽罗问了备细，引到山寨里见了朱武等。\r\n\r\n    三个头领大喜，受了锦袄子并肥羊酒礼，把十两银子赏了庄客，每人吃了十数碗酒，下山同归庄内，见了史进，说道：“山上头领多多上覆”。\r\n\r\n    史进自此常常与朱武等三人往来。\r\n\r\n    不时间，只是王四去山寨里送物事，不只一日。\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'Xiaoluo asked about the preparations, and he led Zhu Wu and others to the cottage. The three heads were overjoyed. They were given a medlar and a feast of sheep&#39;s sake. They paid ten merchants and ten merchants and each had ten bowls of wine. When they went down to the same village, they met Shi Jin and said, “The mountain leader is a lot. Overlay.&quot; Shi Jin has often been with Zhu Wu and other three people since then. No time, only Wang Si went to the cottage to send things, not only one day.', '0');
