INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('f121380f-cc34-46f3-9805-4d8d3a7b0076', '《水浒传》[卷9]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:05:11', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '9', '\r\n    端王又谢了。\r\n\r\n    两个依旧入席。\r\n\r\n    饮宴至暮，尽醉方散。\r\n\r\n    端王相别回宫去了。\r\n\r\n    次日，小王都太尉取出玉龙笔架和两个镇纸玉狮子，着一个小靶子盛了，用黄罗包袱包了，写了一封书呈，却使高俅送去。\r\n\r\n    高俅领了王都尉钧旨，将着两般玉玩器，怀中揣着书呈，迳投端王宫中来。\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', 'End of the king thanked. Both are still seated. Feast to dinner, get drunk. The end of the king did not go back to the palace. On the next day, Xiao Wang was too busy picking up the jade dragon pen holder and two paperweight jade lions. He had a small target, wrapped it up in a yellow bag, and wrote a book, but he sent Gao Hao. Gao Yu led the king’s decree and put together two kinds of jade players. He was carrying a book in his arms.', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('f1387ee9-e8d6-4792-91e8-433850c1ef1c', '《水浒传》[卷62]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 17:08:04', '2018-04-20', '0', '23', '0', '0', '1', '62', '\r\n    “惺惺惜惺惺，好汉识好汉。”\r\n\r\n    史进道：“你们既然如此义气深重，我若送了你们，不是好汉。我放陈达还你，如何？”\r\n\r\n    朱武道：“休得连累了英雄，不当稳便，宁可把我们解官请赏。”\r\n\r\n    史进道：“如何使得。你肯吃我酒食么？”\r\n\r\n    朱武道：“一死尚然不惧，何况酒肉乎！”\r\n', '1b0f4a97-f4ec-4247-9a70-4b28f2a7b9f1', '&quot;But I am sorry, the good man knows the hero.&quot; Shi Jin said: &quot;If you are so loyal, if I sent you, not a hero. I let Chen Da return to you, how?&quot; Zhu Wudao: &quot;Hunt even tired hero, improper stability We would rather dismiss our officials and reward them.” Shi Jindao said: “How to make it. Will you be willing to eat me?” Zhu Wudao: “I&#39;m not afraid of death, not to mention wine and meat!”', '0');
INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('f329b9f2-f720-4646-bec4-669114ee5f17', '《红楼梦》[卷3]', '历史', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-18 10:02:17', '2018-06-12', '0', '433', '0', '0', '1', '3', '天之时，于大荒山无稽崖炼成高十二丈、见方二十四丈大的顽石三万六千五百零一\r\n块。那娲皇只用了三万六千五百块，单单剩下一块未用，弃在青埂峰下。谁知此石\r\n自经锻炼之后，灵性已通，自去自来，可大可小。因见众石俱得补天，独自己无才\r\n不得入选，遂自怨自愧，日夜悲哀。一日正当嗟悼之际，俄见一僧一道远远而来，\r\n', '5e29b80a-8d2a-4642-9900-a32f92b2e57d', 'At the time of the day, in the Da Bingshan Wuji Cliff, it was tempered with thirty-one thousand feet and thirty-four thousand five hundred and forty-one stones. The emperor used only 36,500 pieces, and left the rest of the piece alone and left it under the peak of Qing. Who knows that after this stone has been exercised, spirituality has passed, and self-finding can be great or small. Seeing that all the stones are complemented by the heavens, they are not allowed to be elected only when they are alone, and they mourn themselves and mourn each other day and night. On the occasion of a deafening day, Russia saw a trip from afar.', '0');
