INSERT INTO `p_task` VALUES ('f7eeb3d3-1240-4284-8ed6-f4db8868ce9d', '《斗罗大陆序章》[卷9]', '小说', 'vip', '2afc37a8-3411-48e4-9f60-6b52259acb17', '2018-04-17 16:39:43', '2018-05-26', '0', '400', '0', '0', '1', '9', '\r\n    唐大先生的目光瞬间变冷，全身寒气大盛，瞪视着二长老，“你说谁是叛徒？你见过一个叛徒在得到本门最高秘籍之后会不逃？你见过一个叛徒会以死明志？你见过一个怀有足以毁灭唐门任何高手的绝世暗器却将他作为最后的礼物送给唐门？唐三不是叛徒，他是二百年来，本门最出色的天才。”\r\n\r\n', 'def3130a-a4ae-4589-8f8e-e19cb9c60f29', 'Mr. Tang Dao’s eyes instantly became cold, the whole body was chilly, and he scorned the two elders. “Who are you talking about being a traitor? Have you ever seen a traitor who will not escape after you get the highest secret of the door? You have seen a traitor who will Did you know that you had seen a masterpiece hidden in Tangmen who was capable of destroying any masterpiece of the Tangmen but gave him as a lasting gift to Tangmen? Tang is not a traitor. He is the best genius of the door for 200 years.&quot;', '0');
